              },
              {
                "nextState": null,
                "text": "Exit"
              }
            ],
            "dialogueType": "sendYesNo",
            "text": "Please remember two things. One, this line is actually for overseas shipping, so #rI cannot gurantee exactly which town you'll land#k. Two, since I am putting you in this special flight, it'll be a bit expensive. The service charge is #e#b10,000 mesos#n#k. There's a flight thats about to take off. Are you interested in this direct flight?"
